{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "d715fd23-b520-4b5e-848d-01d0e9f80945", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d715fd23-b520-4b5e-848d-01d0e9f80945@3.pkg/1772597612143/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597612657", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d715fd23-b520-4b5e-848d-01d0e9f80945@3.pkg/1772597612143/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597612657"}, "identifier": "d715fd23-b520-4b5e-848d-01d0e9f80945", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>审题干</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>题干指出 “每一个小人物的参与和行动，汇成大时代的洪流”，这直接表明了社会的发展是由一个个小人物的参与和行动推动的。社会不是抽象的概念，而是由无数具体的个人组成，每个人的行为和选择都在一定程度上影响着社会的发展方向和进程。因此，A 选项是最符合题意的正确答案。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p style=\"margin-left:13.6500pt;\">（改编）小人物从来不是大时代的被动接受者，每一个小人物的参与和行动，汇成大时代的洪流。可见（　　）</p>\n", "title": "（改编）小人物从来不是大时代的被动接受者，每一个小人物的参与和行动，汇成大时代的洪流。可见（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d715fd23-b520-4b5e-848d-01d0e9f80945@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754580354895", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "